&lt;p&gt;Total number of days from19&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; May 2012 to 1&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt; April 2014 = (12 + 30 + 31 + 31 + 30 + 31 + 30 + 31 + 31 + 28 + 31 + 30 + 31 + 30 + 31 + 31 + 30 + 31 + 30 + 31 + 31 + 28 + 31 + 1) = 682&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Total number of odd days = 682/7 = 3 odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, Saturday + 3 = Tuesday.&lt;/p&gt;
Hence, 1&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt; April 2014 was a Tuesday.
